 the froggy lifestyle. Because let's face it - life's too short to NOT be a frog!”<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107550/extras/6be0e56a40bf228bb2facb2a4af58809.poster.avif?t=1736024029\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107550/extras/6be0e56a40bf228bb2facb2a4af58809.webm?t=1736024029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107550/extras/6be0e56a40bf228bb2facb2a4af58809.mp4?t=1736024029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
